input_str: The great Vancouver bash-rock duo Japandroids recently returned to the stage in their hometown, and they’re coming back early next year with the long-awaited new album Near To The Wild Heart Of Life. The album’s title track promises great things. And so it’s great to hear that the band will spend the next few months bringing their heart-surging live shows to venues across the world.
